To use remote push notifications you must first follow the instructions of the "Base integration"


To use remote push messaging with the Neerby SDK, ensure that the 
firebase-messaging
 library is properly specified in your 
app/build.gradle
 dependencies:


{
    implementation 'com.google.firebase:firebase-messaging:17.6.0'
}




...and init the 'google-services' plugin too :


